Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

See Alembic docs: https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/

## NSA Connect — Migration workflow

Configure Alembic (alembic.ini + env.py) **before** creating your first migration.

```bash
cd backend

# Check current migration state
alembic current

# Create a migration after model changes
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe your change"

# Apply all pending migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Roll back one migration
alembic downgrade -1
```

`env.py` reads `DATABASE_URL` from `app.core.config.settings` and imports all
models so autogenerate can detect schema changes.
